    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process for producing wrought iron or steel from pig iron by melting and agitation in a bath followed by working and forging the metal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
